{"tid":2268233,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港」團隊型高質channel 推薦區","createTime":"2020-11-02T15:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T23:31:15.000Z","uid":110080,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e1dfa2161bcd0640c7fbe006d05c701ebe124547","tid":2268233,"uid":110080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:39:33.000Z","msg":"開宗名義 <br />\n呢個post 係希望介紹d 香港高質既團隊型chaneel 比大家<br />\n令更多人認識佢地 <br />\n希望佢地終有一日成為粵語最大既channel <br />\n宣揚香港文化<br />\n所以澳門果d 唔好提<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋介紹得既都係黃 唔洗多講 亦都無需鬥黃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HxoSXzb0pvM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHxoSXzb0pvM&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=3bc697ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HxoSXzb0pvM</a><br />\n<br />\n第一個要介紹既就係近來新開既「試當真」<br />\n<br />\n雖然個channel 開得一陣 但班底大家都唔會陌生<br />\n就係以前captv 既 蘇豪 許賢 遊學修<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱會一星期出幾條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最新出果條輸波教室有以前全盛captv 既味道<br />\n大家可以睇睇岩唔岩你口味<br />\n<br />\n睇好佢地會成為出色既 youtube channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣家處於初創期 大家可以支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aMCPBvfxxKk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaMCPBvfxxKk&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=ba8f4b14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aMCPBvfxxKk</a><br />\n<br />\n第二個要講既就係「小薯茄」<br />\n<br />\n佢地衣家都算香港數一數二既youtube channel<br />\n處於急速上升期 而且係少數老少咸宜既channel<br />\n<br />\n有部份連登仔可能會嫌佢太青少年向<br />\n<br />\n但其實只要睇多幾條佢地片 你就會比佢地成個團隊吸引<br />\n每個幕前都好有特色 一齊果種chemistry so far 無邊個channel 比得上<br />\n<br />\n同埋深入睇佢地唔少片其實都好有意思 唔係真係純for 青少年 <br />\n老實講 就三張既我都睇得好開心 希望大家都可以enjoy<br />\n<br />\n而且佢地成個幕後都係同屆bu 出身 所以拍攝默契同質素都講得上香港數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前黎講最有機會發大黎搞既就係小薯茄 <br />\n完全值得大家更多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抖陣再寫 大家有任何channel 推薦都歡迎提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc3f581a72e29d248bdbc67328b24bfb2690f90","tid":2268233,"uid":223912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:46:51.000Z","msg":"Whizoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fa882e108301badab944c56c9f5f8fa7f83393","tid":2268233,"uid":129644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5525110eaadfaf71ded5be799b54c56b2339d44a","tid":2268233,"uid":161541,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"JFFT"},{"pid":"4a7a50ae87758baf69745914fc5c8eb4da09642e","tid":2268233,"uid":376697,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"仲有好青年荼毒室 搞哲學普及 港台逢星期一晚哲學有計傾都係佢哋拍㗎 手足支持下啦"},{"pid":"c48f50d98b7683f762e76840e30caa99cf07334e","tid":2268233,"uid":129644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"acc3f581a72e29d248bdbc67328b24bfb2690f90","tid":2268233,"uid":223912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T15:46:51.000Z","msg":"Whizoo<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"whizoo 我覺得好麻麻..."},{"pid":"a40a6b31f612650cd4ab50656b13f9afdcaf3502","tid":2268233,"uid":226231,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:13:12.000Z","msg":"armchannel"},{"pid":"f1b5f93bde3f5472c5bf0a8755c5f67e124eb407","tid":2268233,"uid":110080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a7a50ae87758baf69745914fc5c8eb4da09642e","tid":2268233,"uid":376697,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,